South Africa 150 runs, 47.2 overs, 196 minutes, 289 balls, 12x4, 0x6
50 Partnership between Vaughan and Pietersen in 53 minutes, 74 balls, 8x4, 0x6 (Vaughan 30 runs, Pietersen 17 runs, 3 extras)
